@ontos 1.0
@title Product spec example
@type product-spec
@updated 2026-06-05

- Protocol viewer @id(protocol-viewer) #product #viewer
  status: planned
  owner: product
  purpose: Let users inspect large `.ontos` documents in a browser.
  current:
    - Tree navigation, node details, and export actions are required.
    - Editing is not required for the first public release.
  ai_task: Convert requirements into implementation tickets.
  ai_boundary: Preserve protocol compatibility and local-first behavior.
  risk:
    - A viewer without search may not help with large documents.
  verify:
    - Load official examples.
    - Confirm node IDs and references are visible.
  history:
    - 2026-06-05 created official product spec example.

  - Search workflow @id(search-workflow) #search
    status: planned
    depends_on: [[protocol-viewer]]
    acceptance:
      - Search matches node titles.
      - Search matches field values.

    - Empty state @id(empty-state) #ux
      purpose: Show a useful state before a document is loaded.
      verify:
        - Empty state has no broken controls.
